extendedInfo.description: Track My Droid is an easy tool to track your android device. Use this tool when your device is in silent mode and misplaced nearby. This application also helps you in retrieving the current location of the device from any other mobile. It even helps you to send your current location quickly to your selected contacts when you are in emergency situation in just ONE CLICK.TrackMyDroid  provides three main features.â¢Change Sound Settings     This service is used to change your device mode. You can enable or disable silent mode and vibrate mode of your device by sending a secret message to your device from any other mobile. â¢Track Current Location    On receiving secret message to your mobile from other mobile,TrackMyDroid will send back current location to that mobile.For remote installation, user can send default gmail address as a text message to retrieve current location.It send back  message to mobile number and mail to default gmail address.Note:  This feature is limited to android devices having version less than 3.1  Once user set secret message in the app,this feature will be disabled and      retrieve location by sending that message.â¢Emergency help widget     This service helps you to send your current location details along with your predefined help text which is saved.TAGS : Track My Droid, Track, Tracker, My, Your, Droid, Lost Phone, Track Phone, Find Phone, Location, Change Silent, Silent Mode, Where is my Phone,TrackMyDroid, Track Droid, SOS, Send Location, Help , Current Location, Locator, Locate Me, Find, Lost, Phone, My Phone, Locate, Locates, Locator, Tracker, Real Time Tracking, Find Phone, Find Stolen Phone, Find Lost Phone, Seek Droid, Security, Tracker, Whereâs my Droid, Wheres my Droid, Find My Droid, Find My Phone, Droid finder, Phone finder, FindMyDroid, Widgets, Widget, Help Widget, SOS Widget, mobile locate, phone locator seek droid, lookout mobile security, lookout, location, position, misplace, phone, hide
